entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You gathered enough intact Wort bones to restock Entha's supplies.
entries.journal_entry_description: Entha Kandela contracts with creature specialists to trap and kill the larger animals in the area. But traditionally she supplies them with bones to construct their traps. She has run out of bones and needs you to collect some from worrts. She needs five sets of intact bones from tame and normal worrts.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Entha needs to collect bones from older worrts. Kill worrts in the infested areas around the city.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: You seem to have a large enough supply of worrt bones for me. Come on back and I will pay you for them.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: You have Entha's bones. Go back to her for payment.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: You seem to be getting a message from Jabba's Palace.
entries.task06_comm_message_text: If we'd known it would take you this long to get things done we would have just killed you. Speed things up, for your own good!
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Try looking here for some Worrts.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Try looking here for some Worrts.
